2. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The Sinkhorn algorithm is a popular algorithm in machine learning for solving the Optimal Transport problem, and this paper provides an analysis of the algorithm for the UOT problem. 
3. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper provides a computational complexity analysis of the Sinkhorn algorithm, which involves numerical methods for solving optimization problems. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper analyzes the complexity of an algorithm for solving an optimization problem, which falls under the scope of data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with the UOT problem, which has applications in control theory and systems engineering.
